<p>Welcome to the SCP Wiki, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrcali" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6826004); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6826004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604154869" alt="mrcali" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6826004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrcali" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6826004); return false;">mrcali</a></span>.</p>
